com.github.rolecraftdev.guild

Class GuildRank

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.rolecraftdev.guild.GuildRank

  • public final class GuildRank
extends Object
    Represents a player rank within a specific Guild. GuildRanks can be created by the Guild's leader and can have different permissions.
